ight:bold;\"><\/span><\/div><table border><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">Components<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">Final concentration<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">Volume<\/td><\/tr><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">10X PCR Buffer<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">1x<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">2.5 \u03bcL<\/td><\/tr><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">MgCl2 50mM<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">1,0 mM<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">1.5 \u03bcL<\/td><\/tr><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">dNTPs 10 mM Mix<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">2.5 mM<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">1.0 \u03bcL<\/td><\/tr><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">Primers (Reverse and Forward Mix) 2.5 \u00b5M<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">0.1 mM<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">4.0 \u03bcL<\/td><\/tr><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">Ultrapure Water (Milli-Q\u00ae)<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">-<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">13.8 \u03bcL<\/td><\/tr><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">Taq polymerase (5U\/\u00b5L)<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">1.2U\/\u00b5L<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">0.2 \u03bcL<\/td><\/tr><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">DNA template<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">-<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">2.0 \u03bcL<\/td><\/tr><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">Total volume<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">-<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">25 \u03bcL<\/td><\/tr><\/table><div class = \"text-block\"><span>Were used 10X PCR Buffer, MgCl2, Taq Polymerase and dNTPs from Sinapse INC <\/span><span style = \"vertical-align:super;\">\u00ae<\/span><span> (S\u00e3o Paulo - Brazil). Primers are from Integrated DNA Technologies<\/span><span style = \"vertical-align:super;\">\u00ae<\/span><span> (IDT) (Coralville, Iowa, US).<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span style = \"font-weight:bold;\">Thermal Cycler Setup <\/span><\/div><table border><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">Steps<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">Temperature<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">Time<\/td><\/tr><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">Initial denaturation<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">94\u00baC<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">5 min<\/td><\/tr><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">Denaturation<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">94\u00baC<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">1 min<\/td><\/tr><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">Annealing<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">60\u00baC<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">1 min<\/td><\/tr><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" style =\"display : table-cell;\">Elongation<\/td><td rowspan = \"\" colspan = \"\" st